timing_disable_parallel_arcs(25.10)        timing_disable_parallel_arcs(25.10)

Name
       timing_disable_parallel_arcs

Syntax
       timing_disable_parallel_arcs

       {true | false}

       Default: true

       Enables the software to automatically perform reduction of parallel de-
       lay arcs and check arcs to improve efficiency.

       When  set to false, parallel delay and check arc reduction will be dis-
       abled.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

